{"title":"后事早安排","authors":["池北偶　苗地"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"后事早安排"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗　苗地画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据报道，侵越美军当局最近向日本订购四十万个包裹美军尸体的尼龙“尸体袋”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战场上连遭惨败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少爷兵活去死来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中等伤亡”一千多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“轻微损失”六七百。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运不完的尸体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋不尽的棺材。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争继续扩大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后事宜早安排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶紧订制大批尼龙袋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包装从简，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"效率加快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死一个往一只袋里塞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十万只不算多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"够用个一年半载。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}